@NODE FMS1
@TITLE "FMS Limitations"
  1: files larger than 66 kilobytes cannot be packed with the
      evaluation version.

  2: you will only be able to pack one directory at a time,
      if this directory contains subdirectories, FMS will skip
      this subdirectory.
@ENDNODE
